home.name: Rattan Hanging Basket
home.description: Hanging basket in braided rattan with three cords and a metal ring at top. Diameter 6 1/4 in., height 6 1/4 in. Total length approx. 27 1/2 in.

home.name: King/Queen Duvet Cover Set
home.description: King/queen duvet cover set in soft, woven fabric made from a lyocell and cotton blend with a printed pattern. Two pillowcases. Thread count 144.

home.name: Metal Photo Frame
home.description: Frame in clear glass and metal. Slide latch at one side and stand at back. Fits pictures up to 8 x 11 1/2 in. Size of frame 8 1/2 x 12 in.

home.name: Large Cork-lid Scented Candle
home.description: Large scented candle in a glass holder with a cork lid. Diameter 3 1/4 in. Height 6 in. Burn time 80 hours. Scent created in collaboration with perfumers from the renowned Robertet perfume house.

home.name: Large Ceramic Vase
home.description: Large, circular ceramic vase. Diameter 11 3/4 in., total height 12 1/4 in. Diameter of opening 2 1/4 in.

home.name: Small Plant Pot with Bubbles
home.description: Small plant pot in glazed stoneware with a bubbled finish. Inner diameter approx. 3 3/4 in., height 5 in.
